SKT_FIRST.name: Hubby, Captured!
SKT_FIRST.true_desc: Attacks an enemy, and has a <color=#28d9ed>85%</color> chance to increase Priority of the ally with the highest Attack by <color=#28d9ed>10%</color>.
description: Attacks an enemy, and has a <color=#28d9ed>[Buff_C_2000074_1_1]</color> chance to increase Priority of the ally with the highest Attack by <color=#28d9ed>[Buff_V_2000074_1_1]</color>.
SKT_FIRST.true_desc_kr: 적을 공격하고, <color=#28d9ed>85%</color>확률로 공격력이 가장 높은 아군의 행동 게이지를 <color=#28d9ed>10%</color> 증가시킵니다.
SKT_FIRST.true_desc_jp: 敵単体にダメージを与え、<color=#28d9ed>85%</color>の確率で最も攻撃力の高い味方の行動ゲージを<color=#28d9ed>10%</color>UPさせる。

SKT_SECOND.name: I'm Not Letting You Go ♡
SKT_SECOND.true_desc: Attacks all enemies, and recovers Health of all allies by <color=#28d9ed>10%</color>. For each target damaged, increases Priority of the caster by <color=#28d9ed>10%</color>.

SKT_ULTIMATE.name: Blessed Wedding Road
SKT_ULTIMATE.true_desc: Attacks all enemies. Removes all debuffs from all allies and grants Immunity for <color=#28d9ed>2 turn(s)</color>. Recovers Health of all allies by <color=#28d9ed>15%</color>.

SKT_ULTIMATE.name_jp: 祝いのバージンロード
SKT_ULTIMATE.true_desc_kr: 적 전체를 공격합니다. 아군 전체의 모든 약화 효과를 해제하고 <color=#28d9ed>2턴</color> 동안 면역을 부여합니다. 아군 전체의 체력을 <color=#28d9ed>15%</color> 회복시킵니다.
SKT_ULTIMATE.true_desc_jp: 敵全体にダメージを与える。味方全体のすべての弱体効果を解除し、免疫を<color=#28d9ed>2ターン</color>の間付与する。味方全体のHPを<color=#28d9ed>15%</color>回復する。

SKT_CHAIN_PASSIVE.name: Chain Passive
SKT_CHAIN_PASSIVE.true_desc: <color=#ffd732>Chain Starter Effect</color>: After attacking, grants <color=#28d9ed>Find Weakness</color> to all allies for <color=#28d9ed>2 turn(s)</color>.\n\n<color=#ffd732>Dual Attack Effect</color>: After attacking, increases Priority of the ally with the highest Attack by <color=#28d9ed>20%</color>.
